1
00:00:24,030 --> 00:00:25,290
[Adapted from a novel published on Qidian Reading under China Literature]

2
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:27,180
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

3
00:00:28,300 --> 00:00:29,830
[Minors]

4
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:31,550
[should watch with guardian consent]

5
00:02:14,350 --> 00:02:19,430
[Way of Choices]

6
00:02:21,190 --> 00:02:24,600
[Previously]

7
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:22,960
The Demon Lord's artifact!

8
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,960
Once it falls,

9
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,360
there'll be no hope of survival.

10
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,800
You saved my young miss.

11
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,280
Please accept my bow.

12
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,920
If he can fix my meridians,

13
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,320
he can help me change my fate!

14
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:30,329
[Hegu]

15
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,440
Stop following me.

16
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:33,640
I'm not qualified to teach you,

17
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:34,840
nor do I have the time.

18
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,280
Except you,

19
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:39,240
who on the continent
would join this ruin?

20
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,160
I do.

21
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:43,520
I wish to seek your instruction.

22
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:44,960
I may not be able to teach you anything.

23
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:47,360
You'll even suffer
a lot of humiliation and pressure.

24
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:47,960
Sir,

25
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,820
I'm not afraid.

26
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:50,360
Good.

27
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:52,040
This way,

28
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:54,640
we can kill him openly.

29
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,760
Qingteng Banquet is just the beginning.

30
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,760
Together, let's put
the State Religious Academy's name

31
00:02:58,760 --> 00:03:01,290
at the top
of the Imperial Court Exam ranking.

32
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,650
[Tiandao Academy, Building A]

33
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,040
The Qingteng Banquet tonight

34
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,120
is truly lively!

35
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:15,400
The Qingteng Banquet is indeed lively!

36
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:18,600
It's almost like
the Great Tribal Gathering of Red River.

37
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:23,040
The Great Zhou respects tradition,

38
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,500
of course it will be grand.

39
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,920
Only students of Qingteng League Academies

40
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:27,250
are qualified to enter.

41
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,890
Which academy are you from?

42
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,520
We're from the State Religious Academy.

43
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,980
State Religious Academy?

44
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,530
You mean that ruined place?

45
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,560
I heard

46
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:38,160
they recently recruited a useless fool
who can't cultivate.

47
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,160
Is it you?

48
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,480
Open your eyes and look closely,

49
00:03:41,550 --> 00:03:42,920
you are not on the list!

50
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:42,980
[Institute of Rituals]
[Qingyao Thirteen Divisions]

51
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,250
[Tiandao Academy] [The Li Palace Affiliate]
[Zhaixing Academy]

52
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:45,240
The Great Zhou

53
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,760
was founded on the State Religion.

54
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:50,560
The Founding Emperor honored it
as the head of Six Qingteng Academies.

55
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,120
Yet you speak of it with such contempt.

56
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,480
What are your intentions?

57
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:54,600
How dare you

58
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,320
claim to be the head?

59
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,520
Taste my fist!

60
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,240
I—

61
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,360
I can't move.

62
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,000
Senior Huanyu!

63
00:04:05,690 --> 00:04:07,740
[Zhuang Huanyu,
Top Genius of Tiandao Academy]

64
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:09,120
The Qingteng Banquet is for students
to exchange ideas.

65
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,980
Why did you hurt him for no reason?

66
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,920
This Senior has a flushed face

67
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:15,920
and mouth ulcers.

68
00:04:15,970 --> 00:04:17,839
It's a symptom of Liver-Heat Depression.

69
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,600
I merely gave him acupuncture
to reduce his internal heat.

70
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:19,959
You—

71
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:24,260
Do you feel your Qi and blood
flowing more smoothly now?

72
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,540
I'm... indeed more comfortable now.

73
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,200
Mystical nonsense!

74
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:34,740
Junior Sister,

75
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,800
why are you with this poor boy?

76
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,400
Who are you?

77
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,140
I'm Zhuang Huanyu.

78
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,180
I sat next to you

79
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:45,360
when the director gave his lecture.

80
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:49,450
If you wish to attend the Banquet,

81
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:51,560
you are always welcome at Tiandao Academy.

82
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:54,230
Mr. Huanyu is the top genius
of Tiandao Academy!

83
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,280
I am a disciple
of the State Religious Academy.

84
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,710
Of course I am with Sir.

85
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:01,440
Sir?

86
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,960
You must have been deceived by him.

87
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:06,490
I will seek justice for you!

88
00:05:06,530 --> 00:05:08,100
Stop pestering my student.

89
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:14,040
The Qingteng Banquet is a rehearsal
for the Imperial Court Exam,

90
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:17,360
where famous academies showcase skills
and exchange ideas.

91
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,420
There is no doubt how important it is.

92
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,510
Junior Sister,

93
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:22,360
he's not qualified to take you inside.

94
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,820
Don't hold yourself back!

95
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:24,800
You—

96
00:05:24,820 --> 00:05:27,080
Director Mao Qiuyu has arrived!

97
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,640
According to tradition,

98
00:05:29,770 --> 00:05:31,170
State Religious Academy

99
00:05:31,470 --> 00:05:33,480
is indeed qualified to attend.

100
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,980
Greetings, Director.

101
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:36,400
Everyone,

102
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:37,970
please take your seats.

103
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:46,080
Where are the pastries?

104
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:50,680
How dare they give you
such a shabby table, Sir?

105
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:51,440
It's fine.

106
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,720
Since we are here, let us be at peace.

107
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,720
See what happens.

108
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:55,640
Fine.

109
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,250
I'll listen to you, Sir.

110
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,470
That brat Chen Changsheng

111
00:06:06,490 --> 00:06:08,210
actually reopened
the State Religious Academy.

112
00:06:08,210 --> 00:06:10,560
He's humiliating Her Majesty and you!

113
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:11,880
I heard

114
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:14,340
a peasant from the mountains,

115
00:06:14,370 --> 00:06:16,160
a useless fool without training,

116
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:18,240
reopened the State Religious Academy?

117
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,200
That academy was abolished
by my grandaunt,

118
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:22,400
Holy Empress Tianhai, herself!

119
00:06:21,340 --> 00:06:24,180
[Tianhai Ya'er,
Young Master of Tianhai family]

120
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,440
What you did

121
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:26,200
is humiliating the Tianhai family!

122
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,850
So you are Chen Changsheng?

123
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:34,770
Come up here.

124
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,600
I'm going to kill you!

125
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,680
Kneel and beg me,

126
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,280
and maybe I will leave your body intact.

127
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:44,320
Qingteng Banquet is for the six academies
to exchange ideas.

128
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:45,920
What business is it of the Tianhai family?

129
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:49,320
The entire divine capital Shendu
is ruled by the Tianhai family.

130
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:50,380
Qingteng Banquet?

131
00:06:50,590 --> 00:06:51,750
It's nothing.

132
00:06:52,090 --> 00:06:53,880
-Who is she?
-Who is this little brat

133
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,230
daring to offend the Tianhai family?

134
00:06:55,230 --> 00:06:57,100
Is it because
he's the Holy Empress's grandnephew

135
00:06:57,100 --> 00:06:58,700
that no one dares to stop him?

136
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,250
So the Great Zhou

137
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:07,610
has already rotted to this extent.

138
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,510
Quiet!

139
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,000
What?

140
00:07:15,320 --> 00:07:17,200
Am I not allowed to laugh
at Qingteng Banquet?

141
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,640
What's so funny?

142
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:19,880
Say it out loud

143
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,560
so I can enjoy it too?

144
00:07:22,100 --> 00:07:23,180
I thought

145
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:26,000
the Qingteng Banquet
was the most cherished tradition
of the Qingteng Academies.

146
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:25,850
[Xuanyuan Po, Zhaixing Academy]

147
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:28,130
I didn't expect
that when someone causes trouble,

148
00:07:28,130 --> 00:07:29,860
you wouldn't even dare to fart!

149
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,080
If

150
00:07:32,340 --> 00:07:34,020
I kill you now,

151
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:36,050
will you still be able to laugh?

152
00:07:39,190 --> 00:07:39,750
Don't!

153
00:07:40,770 --> 00:07:42,080
Kneel and apologize now!

154
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,370
He's from the Tianhai family,

155
00:07:43,370 --> 00:07:44,490
don't drag us down with you!

156
00:07:44,490 --> 00:07:45,020
Exactly!

157
00:07:46,659 --> 00:07:47,970
I joined the Zhaixing Academy

158
00:07:47,970 --> 00:07:50,030
because it has the strongest spirit.

159
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,290
You may fear him,

160
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,480
but I don't!

161
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:55,800
Please wait.

162
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:57,900
Thank you for earlier.

163
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,400
But he is indeed
the Holy Empress's grandnephew.

164
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,000
If you go,

165
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:02,640
you'll be in trouble.

166
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:04,520
I'm from the Red River Mountains.

167
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:06,120
Mountain folk are never afraid of trouble,

168
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,520
nor do we bow to villains!

169
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:09,320
I'm also from the mountains.

170
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:11,400
Two peasants from the mountains,

171
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:13,920
I'll burn your mountains to the ground!

172
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:14,930
Don't worry.

173
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,400
He's in the Realm of Seated Illumination,

174
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,400
and I am, too.

175
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,200
You have no cultivation,

176
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,530
I'll go up and fight him.

177
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,640
I'm confident I can win.

178
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,600
He actually dares to go up.

179
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,960
If you offended the Tianhai family,

180
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:25,380
your future is over!

181
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:26,350
Xuanyuan Po

182
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,680
of the Zhaixing Academy,

183
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,600
please enlighten me!

184
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,880
I love tough bones the most.

185
00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:33,000
The tougher they are,

186
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,860
the better it feels to crush them!

187
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:35,860
You want to die?

188
00:08:41,780 --> 00:08:43,230
[Destiny Star, Wind Zhen]

189
00:08:45,230 --> 00:08:46,360
Watch out, Big Guy!

190
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:52,000
Useless fool at the initial Realm
of Seated Illumination,

191
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,810
you dare to fight me?

192
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,060
He can trigger the force of a hurricane

193
00:09:06,060 --> 00:09:07,460
with just one punch!

194
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:08,390
Sir,

195
00:09:08,420 --> 00:09:09,990
the big guy is going to lose!

196
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:11,000
No.

197
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:13,890
Tianhai Ya'er's attack seems to be fierce,

198
00:09:13,890 --> 00:09:15,540
but his footwork is unstable.

199
00:09:15,540 --> 00:09:16,140
Besides,

200
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,840
the big guy
hasn't used his full strength yet.

201
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,850
He might surprise everyone.

202
00:09:29,740 --> 00:09:31,900
[Xuanyuan Po, Beastification]

203
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,030
Beastification?

204
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:32,000
He's a Yao!

205
00:09:32,070 --> 00:09:33,140
The body transforms

206
00:09:33,140 --> 00:09:34,340
and strength doubles,

207
00:09:34,340 --> 00:09:36,240
this is the unique skill of their race!

208
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,520
You're amazing, Sir.

209
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,800
You saw through the situation long ago.

210
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,640
As expected of a son of Red River!

211
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:42,810
At the same cultivation realm,

212
00:09:42,810 --> 00:09:43,460
Yao

213
00:09:43,700 --> 00:09:46,230
have the advantage
of their beastification.

214
00:10:02,690 --> 00:10:04,100
Yao?

215
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:05,800
Great!

216
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,320
Their strong vitality

217
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:09,980
makes torturing them even more satisfying!

218
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:13,910
Something is wrong.

219
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:28,600
My arms are losing feeling!

220
00:10:28,690 --> 00:10:29,330
Is this...

221
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:30,520
Poison?

222
00:10:30,770 --> 00:10:31,720
It's Zhen Poison!

223
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,640
He used poison!

224
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:33,900
Such a dirty trick!

225
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:35,360
Is no one going to stop him?

226
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:39,020
The Zhen Poison

227
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,740
is triggered by True Essence.

228
00:10:40,740 --> 00:10:42,760
It corrodes the meridians
and acupuncture points.

229
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:45,020
The victim will be disabled, if not dead.

230
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:48,490
[Institute of Rituals]
[Qingyao Thirteen Divisions]
[Tiandao Academy]

231
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:49,100
[The Li Palace Affiliate]
[Zhaixing Academy]

232
00:10:55,620 --> 00:10:57,460
Today's top prize!

233
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:08,010
The poison is spreading
throughout his entire body,

234
00:11:08,010 --> 00:11:09,670
I have to stop it immediately.

235
00:11:10,210 --> 00:11:11,010
Needle Hegu,

236
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:11,720
Quchi,

237
00:11:11,930 --> 00:11:13,060
and then Zhongting!

238
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,170
Fortunately, it's stopped in time.

239
00:11:15,170 --> 00:11:16,680
But it will take some time

240
00:11:16,850 --> 00:11:18,440
for the posion to be neutralized.

241
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:20,640
No one can cure my Zhen Poison.

242
00:11:21,130 --> 00:11:22,600
Do you think

243
00:11:22,620 --> 00:11:24,120
a peasant like you can actually save him?

244
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:26,200
You're just humiliating yourself!

245
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:28,060
If Sir says it can be cured,

246
00:11:28,060 --> 00:11:29,190
then it can be cured!

247
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:33,310
You're quite pretty.

248
00:11:33,470 --> 00:11:34,410
How about

249
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:35,840
I play with you first,

250
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:37,580
and then kill him,

251
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:40,360
and then come back
to keep playing with you?

252
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,360
What do you think?

253
00:11:42,580 --> 00:11:44,430
Zhongshan Storm Sword, Third Style:

254
00:11:44,430 --> 00:11:45,340
Gather Qi in the Yang Meridians,

255
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:46,670
unleash the True Essence

256
00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:48,270
to trigger a thousand waves!

257
00:11:53,670 --> 00:11:54,930
You disgusting thing,

258
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:57,620
I'll whip that filthy mouth
right off your face!

259
00:11:57,970 --> 00:11:59,170
How is that possible?

260
00:11:59,810 --> 00:12:00,610
Fourth Style:

261
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:02,010
Circulate the Sea of Qi,

262
00:12:02,010 --> 00:12:03,490
poise True Essence at the shoulders

263
00:12:03,490 --> 00:12:05,020
to cleave the rain curtain!

264
00:12:07,950 --> 00:12:08,680
Fifth Style:

265
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,370
Open the hidden organs to the mystic,

266
00:12:10,370 --> 00:12:11,450
channel True Essence internally

267
00:12:11,450 --> 00:12:13,110
to shake the wind and thunder!

268
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:18,420
You

269
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:19,440
are too weak.

270
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:26,920
Young Master!

271
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:29,750
Gosh!

272
00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:30,830
Three moves?

273
00:12:31,260 --> 00:12:32,320
She defeated Tianhai Ya'er in three moves,

274
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:34,720
and he's ranked 30th
on the Blue Cloud List!

275
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:36,070
Who is she?

276
00:12:36,270 --> 00:12:38,330
Why have we never heard of her before?

277
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,570
Young Master,

278
00:12:46,590 --> 00:12:47,730
Are you hurt?

279
00:12:49,140 --> 00:12:49,920
Get lost!

280
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,530
You're just two peasants,

281
00:12:51,620 --> 00:12:52,550
low-lives,

282
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:54,000
how dare you wound me!

283
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,720
Chen Changsheng,

284
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,190
I have decided!

285
00:12:57,560 --> 00:12:58,600
I'll turn this peasant

286
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:00,020
into a human vase.

287
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:01,900
Then I'll kill you.

288
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:02,810
And finally,

289
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:05,000
I'll cripple that Tang Thirty-Six!

290
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:08,920
I know you're angry.

291
00:13:09,370 --> 00:13:10,650
But so what?

292
00:13:11,010 --> 00:13:13,070
I am the Holy Empress's grandnephew.

293
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,650
Killing you

294
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:17,000
is like trampling on ants on the ground!

295
00:13:28,130 --> 00:13:29,730
You are wrong about two things.

296
00:13:29,730 --> 00:13:30,550
First,

297
00:13:30,730 --> 00:13:32,400
I'm not without cultivation.

298
00:13:32,700 --> 00:13:33,470
Second,

299
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:36,170
no matter who you are,

300
00:13:38,060 --> 00:13:40,520
if you want to hurt my friend
and my disciple,

301
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:42,500
I will destroy you first!

302
00:13:45,690 --> 00:13:47,790
[Attending a Banquet, Destroying a Man]

303
00:13:47,810 --> 00:13:51,480
[The Young Director: Episode 4]

304
00:14:01,290 --> 00:14:02,290
Chen Changsheng,

305
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:05,130
how dare you destroy his Sea of Qi!

306
00:14:05,340 --> 00:14:06,300
Guards!

307
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,800
Arrest

308
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:09,000
these two offenders!

309
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:10,990
Stand down.

310
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,700
Outsiders are not allowed

311
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:15,210
to act insolently

312
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:16,770
at the Qingteng Banquet.

313
00:14:16,770 --> 00:14:18,390
You used Tianhai Ya'er

314
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,920
as a tool for your own gain.

315
00:14:21,060 --> 00:14:22,860
Do you think

316
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:25,550
that Her Majesty
can't see through your despicable tactics?

317
00:14:25,550 --> 00:14:26,450
I was—

318
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,960
I was only trying
to help share Her Majesty's burdens!

319
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:29,840
Fool!

320
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:33,290
Her Majesty has sharp eyes.

321
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:35,080
Without her permission,

322
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:38,720
how could the State Religious Academy
have been reopened?

323
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:40,320
You should know

324
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:42,460
who will be held responsible.

325
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:48,320
The night of Shendu

326
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:51,600
can kill people easily.

327
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:56,760
That night,

328
00:14:57,880 --> 00:15:00,080
the Qingteng Banquet ended in discord.

329
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:02,700
[State Religious Academy]
[Institute of Rituals]
[Qingyao Thirteen Divisions]

330
00:15:00,560 --> 00:15:01,560
Although the State Religious Academy

331
00:15:01,560 --> 00:15:02,730
rejoined the Six Qingteng Academies

332
00:15:02,730 --> 00:15:05,060
[Tiandao Academy]
[The Li Palace Affiliate]
[Zhaixing Academy]

333
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:05,520
and gained entry
to the Imperial Court Exam,

334
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:06,560
no one was happy.

335
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:09,070
As if

336
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:11,440
we're the ones who did wrong.

337
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:14,300
But does no one really care

338
00:15:15,050 --> 00:15:16,980
about the call from the mountains?

339
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:24,200
Senior...

340
00:15:31,060 --> 00:15:31,780
Big Guy...

341
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:49,170
I know

342
00:15:49,210 --> 00:15:50,660
they don't mean it.

343
00:15:52,030 --> 00:15:54,440
They just fear I might
implicate the entire academy

344
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:56,240
after I offended the Tianhai family.

345
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:56,760
So

346
00:15:57,370 --> 00:15:58,730
what's your next plan?

347
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:01,320
My fellow villagers pooled their money

348
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:02,120
to send me here to Shendu

349
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:03,040
to study.

350
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,920
I must earn the money back

351
00:16:04,870 --> 00:16:08,850
[I must earn the money back
before I return home,]

352
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:07,750
before I return home,

353
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:09,360
even if I have to sweep or wash dishes.

354
00:16:08,870 --> 00:16:11,450
[even if I have to sweep or wash dishes...
Xuanyuan Po]

355
00:16:10,560 --> 00:16:12,840
Did you come all this way to Shendu

356
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:14,890
to sweep the floor and wash dishes?

357
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:17,070
If you have nowhere to go,

358
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:19,080
come with us
to the State Religious Academy!

359
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:21,480
You can
still take the Imperial Court Exam.

360
00:16:21,550 --> 00:16:22,240
Although

361
00:16:22,490 --> 00:16:23,950
we only have a ruined yard,

362
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:25,560
perhaps you will like it.

363
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,440
That place

364
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,610
is as free as the mountains.

365
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:36,640
Great!

366
00:16:36,730 --> 00:16:38,130
Now there are three of us!

367
00:16:39,820 --> 00:16:42,870
[Great manors veil the endless night;
But faint sparks will ignite the sky.]

368
00:16:49,370 --> 00:16:50,400
Congratulations!

369
00:16:50,400 --> 00:16:51,600
You have become the third student

370
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:53,400
of the State Religious Academy!

371
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:58,000
Are there any rules for joining?

372
00:16:58,160 --> 00:16:59,820
Whatever Sir says is the rule.

373
00:17:00,560 --> 00:17:02,840
There are no directors or teachers?

374
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,450
Sir is the director,

375
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,760
Sir is the teacher,

376
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:08,319
and Sir is also a student.

377
00:17:08,359 --> 00:17:09,410
Three in one!

378
00:17:09,599 --> 00:17:12,480
Therefore,
Sir is the State Religious Academy itself.

379
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,839
Then I shall learn from him.

380
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:14,700
I'll teach you!

381
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:16,119
Sir is my master,

382
00:17:16,170 --> 00:17:18,230
and that makes him your grandmaster!

383
00:17:21,040 --> 00:17:21,730
I heard

384
00:17:21,839 --> 00:17:23,500
you destroyed Tianhai Ya'er.

385
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:24,319
Well done!

386
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:26,359
This deserves a grand celebration!

387
00:17:26,359 --> 00:17:27,079
Haven't seen you for a few days,

388
00:17:27,079 --> 00:17:28,240
and the academy is growing.

389
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:29,070
New students?

390
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,420
This is my friend.

391
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:31,550
I'm Tang Thirty-Six

392
00:17:31,760 --> 00:17:33,400
from the Tang family of Wenshui!

393
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:33,920
Hello!

394
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:35,520
You can call me Luo.

395
00:17:35,690 --> 00:17:36,890
I'm Xuanyuan Po.

396
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:42,680
By the way,

397
00:17:42,950 --> 00:17:45,410
why didn't I see you
at the Qingteng Banquet?

398
00:17:45,570 --> 00:17:46,610
Those old geezers

399
00:17:46,840 --> 00:17:48,100
locked me up all night.

400
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:48,820
Otherwise,

401
00:17:48,860 --> 00:17:51,660
you wouldn't have had the chance
to make your move!

402
00:17:52,560 --> 00:17:53,550
Bad news.

403
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,690
A grand celebration will be held
at Weiyang Palace

404
00:17:55,690 --> 00:17:57,760
for the Qixi Festival tomorrow night.

405
00:17:57,760 --> 00:17:58,660
The Lishan Sword Sect

406
00:17:58,660 --> 00:18:00,800
will propose marriage
to the Divine General's Estate.

407
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:02,130
Your fiancée Xu Yourong

408
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:03,690
is going to get married.

409
00:18:15,900 --> 00:18:17,900
[At Qingming, Paulownia flowers bloom
as the first rainbows appear.]

410
00:18:17,900 --> 00:18:20,480
[The spring vows of lovers
are no match for a page of fate.]

411
00:18:26,090 --> 00:18:30,050
[To be continued]

412
00:18:32,190 --> 00:18:33,280
You've been watching for so long,

413
00:18:33,280 --> 00:18:35,120
why not join the State Religious Academy?

414
00:18:35,120 --> 00:18:37,520
Remember to scan the code
to register here!

415
00:18:38,730 --> 00:18:41,980
[In the next episode]

416
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,400
The union of North and South

417
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:42,320
is vital to the future of the Human Race.

418
00:18:42,320 --> 00:18:43,840
You are far too insignificant

419
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:45,500
compared to this grand cause!

420
00:18:45,600 --> 00:18:46,480
Why

421
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:48,340
is everyone guarding against me?

422
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:50,040
No matter what trap you have set,

423
00:18:50,040 --> 00:18:52,080
Sir will break it in front of your eyes!

424
00:18:52,080 --> 00:18:53,840
Interesting kid.

425
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,360
However,

426
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:56,920
what was once the Gate of Life,

427
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:59,200
is now the Gate of Death.

